HEADWORD: Bottled
<hw>Bot"tled</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Put
into bottles; inclosed in bottles; pent up in, or as in, a
bottle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having the shape of a bottle; protuberant.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

